Package: subfinder
Version: 2.14.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: recon
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/subfinder
Description: Fast passive subdomain enumeration tool
 Subfinder is a subdomain discovery tool that uses passive sources
 (certificate transparency, DNS data, search engines, etc.) to find
 valid subdomains for a target domain.
